<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>上门为老人办理了居民医保</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>相关调查正在进行中</span></strong></span></p>
